unittitle_ssm: Socialist Party (U.S.) New York (N.Y.) Letter Books
abstract_ssm: The New York City local was the largest such unit of the Socialist Party (U.S.). The collection consists of 151 subject files that include correspondence, reports on electoral activities, membership records, branch records, committee papers, financial papers, minutes, form letters, miscellaneous printed matter, resolutions, and convention reports.
